{"tid":2472024,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"真·三國無雙 ︱林雪神還原董卓　呻拍攝辛苦：我騎嗰隻馬中暑走咗","createTime":"2021-04-02T05:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T15:18:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":125,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9863679e425597d0b9ec1800ddeb43da71e5c7","tid":2472024,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"林雪周四（1日）出席電影《七人樂隊》首映，談起是次角色他就指：「一個痴線、有啲病嘅人，但平時又好正經，其實只係做返自己，我就係嗰個人。」所以今次角色對他而言完全沒有難度。<br />\n<br />\n提起由周顯揚執導、杜致朗編劇，耗資超過三億港元製作，改編自經典電玩遊戲的電影《真．三國無雙 》定於4月29日正式上映，在電影飾演董卓的林雪早前被大讚入型入格：「我自己都覺得似先拍，如果唔係都唔拍。」<br />\n<br />\n林雪又大爆拍攝期間好辛苦：「熱、啲衫好重、要騎馬打仗，聽講我騎嗰隻馬第日中咗暑走咗，心裏面都唔太安樂。」 談起Netflix以破華語片記錄的8位數天價購入電影版權，預定在暑假期間上架，林雪興奮大讚：「Netflix真係有眼光！（有分紅？）分享喜悅就有，唔鍾意分紅、鍾意分享喜悅。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210401/454435909257924608507924.jpeg/9AubaLnqSH5b5VMKM573H99nSnX0urMSsXNjrbFzY60?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210401%2F454435909257924608507924.jpeg%2F9AubaLnqSH5b5VMKM573H99nSnX0urMSsXNjrbFzY60%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=bf27d386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210401/454360033996574720057326.jpeg/vdCGNbRIfUP-f3k7xzvLfDek5o_0c3Pru7aR97u2kfc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210401%2F454360033996574720057326.jpeg%2FvdCGNbRIfUP-f3k7xzvLfDek5o_0c3Pru7aR97u2kfc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f552c879&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"451687b29c6d6dc018068b24fad9981267390e8d","tid":2472024,"uid":38528,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"董卓會唔會講粗口?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812f230ce60fe6624fb4a1db8be2642a66048d3e","tid":2472024,"uid":185651,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"爛口董卓 <img src=